#Command Briefing

$Stage Text:
 XSTR("We are at the threshold. Behind us lies the nebula. Ahead, the Beta Aquilae system. And hopefully, the Alliance.", -1)
$end_multi_text
$Ani Filename: <default>
+Wave Filename: none

$Stage Text:
 XSTR("But the Shivans aren't letting us leave without a fight. Sensors show a blockade force at the node. Two cruisers. Heavy fighter cover.", -1)
$end_multi_text
$Ani Filename: <default>
+Wave Filename: none

$Stage Text:
 XSTR("This is it. We punch through, or we die here.", -1)
$end_multi_text
$Ani Filename: <default>
+Wave Filename: none


