$Multi text
    XSTR("We made it. The nebula is behind us. The stars... the stars look different here. Beta Aquilae. We are back in Terran space. But we're not safe yet. We're picking up distress signals from the local garrison. The war followed us home.", -1)
$end_multi_text
$Voice: none.wav
